com.google.gcloud.datastore

Interface QueryResult<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of the results value.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterator<V>

    public interface QueryResult<V>
extends Iterator<V>
    The result of a Google Cloud Datastore query submission. When result is not typed it is possible to cast it to its appropriate type according to the resultClass() value. Results are loaded lazily therefore it is possible to get a DatastoreServiceException upon hasNext or next calls.
